<br>
Foreman Tunic is 0.0 wt and Spore Covered is only 0.4 wt.<br>
<br>
What kind of bags and food/water do you carry to get that much weight?<br>
<br>
&quot;What is a typicaly inexpensive light 2hb to practice ($100 pp or less)? I use a PSU for h2h but it is heavy and slow.&quot;<br>
<br>
If you consider 1.1wt heavy for a weapon then you're not going to like 2hb at all.<br>
<br>
Bamboo Bo Stick 8/20 1.0wt<br>
Adamantite Bo Stick 19/30 6.5 wt.  Procs Lightning Storm starting at 30.<br>
I see both going 50-150pp.<br>
<br>
&quot;What is an inexpensive face and belt for me?&quot;<br>
<br>
Face: Foresaken Pariah Mask 5ac 0.4wt free ultra-common drop from iksar pariah.  Silvery Mask 5ac 25hps 0.2 wt clickable Identify at 25, 50pp.<br>
<br>
Waist: Spider Fur Belt 10ac 40hps 5agi/dex 0.0wt 200-400pp.  Anything cheaper would be a downgrade from the TBB. <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/unorpin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Norpin</A> at: 9/13/02 11:24:08 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccccc><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/umaewyn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Maewyn</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Young Grasshoppah</span><br>  Posts: 6<br> <font color=#8b1a1a>(9/13/02 11:24:00 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1877.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Another couple questions...</span><hr size=1> Thank you Norpin.  Question about the Adam. Bo Stick.  The proc (which I am far from procing I am sure) is an AE?  Is the proc suicidal?  Heard it was from my brother but he is a 60 bard so....<br>
